    "body": "Hi! I think you could add a custom command to your starship.toml file that should look something like this: [custom.rust_custom] and define the command, format and when options. For the command option you define which command to run, the format option is the you you are looking for and when is for when to be run. For instance you run **rustc --version** or you can add whatever arguments to the command you d like and in the format you define how you d like it to appear. You can look it up for more info but this is the starting point.",
